@startuml Logo Comparison Flow

title Use Case 3 - Logo Infringement Check (Optional)

autonumber
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ParticipantPadding 25
skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam ResponseMessageBelowArrow true

actor Lawyer
participant "REST API" as API
participant "Logo Check Service" as LogoService
participant "Logo Preprocessing" as LogoPreprocess
participant "Logo Feature Extractor" as FeatureExtractor
participant "Visual Similarity Engine" as VisualSimilarity
database "Trademark DB" as DB
participant "Async Job Queue" as Queue
participant "External Online Search Worker" as Worker
participant "External Online Sources" as Sources
participant "Result Delivery Service" as Delivery

Lawyer -> API: Submit reference logo + suspicious logo
API -> API: Validate request
API -> LogoService: Start logo comparison

LogoService -> LogoPreprocess: Normalize both logo files
LogoPreprocess --> LogoService: Prepared visual inputs

LogoService -> FeatureExtractor: Extract visual features and text-in-logo if available
FeatureExtractor --> LogoService: Feature vectors

LogoService -> DB: Find Top-200 internal logo candidates
DB --> LogoService: Internal logo candidates
loop For each internal logo candidate
  LogoService -> VisualSimilarity: Compare reference logo with internal candidate
  VisualSimilarity --> LogoService: Visual similarity score
end

LogoService -> LogoService: Build Top-200 internal ranking
API -> Queue: Create async external logo search job
Queue --> Worker: Deliver job

Worker -> Sources: Search online external sources for logo candidates
Sources --> Worker: External logo candidates
loop For each external logo candidate
  Worker -> VisualSimilarity: Compare reference logo with external candidate
  VisualSimilarity --> Worker: Visual similarity score
end
Worker -> Worker: Build Top-200 external ranking
Worker -> Delivery: Send delayed external logo result set
Delivery --> API: Top-200 external logo results (later)
API --> Lawyer: External logo enrichment update

LogoService --> API: Top-200 internal logo results
API --> Lawyer: Top-200 internal logo results (fast) + visual summary

@enduml

